# Per-install generated agent CLAUDE.md lives under agents/ (already ignored
# above). The root CLAUDE.md and seed-agents/*/CLAUDE.md are product templates
# and MUST be tracked, so do NOT ignore CLAUDE.md globally.

# Custom MCP servers and config (user-specific)
mcp-servers/
.mcp.json
mcp-catalog.local.json

# Personal/project-specific docs (not part of the product)
